{"tid":768510,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"返工遇到既奇人奇事","createTime":"2018-08-05T12:45:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-05T12:45:15.000Z","uid":100331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8cd70d026272d3c08f6e82dcbe42a730ad879af8","tid":768510,"uid":100331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T12:45:15.000Z","msg":"返call centre 有某幾個客成日都打上黎<br />\n一個成日打上黎問問題 態度好差咁問<br />\n如果同事唔識答 或者對佢惡少少 就會爆炸搵經理<br />\n因為佢要投訴人 搵野投訴<br />\n每隔一星期就打上黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另一個客 一打上黎要人地喂一聲就cut 線 唔喂唔會cut<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 聽同事講由201幾年打到而家仲打緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有個打上黎 口齒不清 唔知佢講咩 <br />\n但你都要交足戲咁問佢野 聽佢野<br />\n奇奇怪怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n想知其他工有啲咩奇怪人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}